title: LENNY MIKA
description:
Hi, I'm Lenny Mika! (he/him) 

ABOUT
Lenny Mika is a Berlin based Writer, Author, and Storyteller. 

He wants to inspire people through "words, lines, and everything in between." which is why he shares the most personal experiences of life in his writings. He isn't afraid of sharing his deepest feelings, neither does he need a mask to tell his story. 

Writing has always been Lenny Mika's safe haven, and he thrives for his writings to have a similar effect on others. Raw, unfiltered, perfectly imperfect - for individuals to relate to and resonate with. 

Because writing saves lives.
